                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://lucene.markmail.org/message/srbnucwor6kyxv2e?q=ContentStream+refactor&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://lucene.markmail.org/message/srbnucwor6kyxv2e?q=ContentStream+refactor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

